to save the day.

07:00.788 --> 07:04.289
Become a big
worldwide star.

07:04.291 --> 07:07.225
Yeah.

07:07.227 --> 07:08.627
Did i say that
out loud?

07:08.629 --> 07:10.262
Yeah.

07:10.264 --> 07:11.430
