of where we're supposed to be.

07:43.130 --> 07:44.629
I'm not
cycling ahead.

07:44.631 --> 07:46.164
- You got to focus, okay?
- I'm focused.

07:46.166 --> 07:47.466
- Focus, baby.
- I'm totally focused.

07:47.468 --> 07:48.733
And then we're gonna
go to belgium.

07:48.735 --> 07:49.968
We're gonna kill it...

07:49.970 --> 07:51.002
That's what
i'm talking about.

07:51.004 --> 07:52.404
One last time

07:52.406 --> 07:53.405
And then turn the band
over to gigi.

07:53.407 --> 07:54.739
Honey...
[sighs]

07:54.741 --> 07:56.341
