dulli and grohl and all these--

08:00.747 --> 08:01.913
Dulli stole my vibe.

08:01.915 --> 08:03.281
Dulli did not
steal your vibe.

08:03.283 --> 08:04.416
Oh, my god.
You're gonna deny that now?

08:04.418 --> 08:06.017
Oh, what are you
talking about?

08:06.019 --> 08:07.586
You've got two pictures
of the man on your wall.

08:07.588 --> 08:09.588
