steal your vibe, baby.

08:12.993 --> 08:16.361
You hijacked your own vibe
out of bitterness and resentment

08:16.363 --> 08:17.762
Because the world
wasn't working

08:17.764 --> 08:19.598
The way you thought
it was going to.

08:19.600 --> 08:23.168
Maybe it wasn't happening
because of gigi.

08:23.170 --> 08:25.303
She is bringing us everything
that we ever wanted...

08:25.305 --> 08:26.304
