a second career in europe?

08:31.945 --> 08:33.345
If i do this right,
every summer,

08:33.347 --> 08:35.447
We could go over and do,
like, six or seven gigs.

08:35.449 --> 08:39.451
We'd be going to paris,
london, italy.

08:39.453 --> 08:41.486
Mm...
Italy?

08:41.488 --> 08:43.788
Venice, positano--
how cool would that be?

08:43.790 --> 08:46.124
