<i>we</i> can do this.

08:56.904 --> 08:58.403
Okay, then let's do it.

09:00.641 --> 09:02.073
Your voice, my ass.

09:02.075 --> 09:03.842
Let's take europe
by storm.

09:03.844 --> 09:05.644
How do i know
you're not lying?

09:05.646 --> 09:07.178
Why would i lie
about this?

09:07.180 --> 09:08.847
Because you're sober.

09:08.849 --> 09:10.682
Well, actually i'm still
a little hung over.

09:10.684 --> 09:13.351
[giggles]

09:13.353 --> 09:14.986
That's completely true.

09:14.988 --> 09:18.990
I mean, watching your dad
onstage, that is a master class.

09:18.992 --> 09:22.193
That guy's got all the tools
it takes to be a big star,

09:22.195 --> 09:24.996
