you know,

09:40.047 --> 09:42.847
But famous for being good,
you know?

09:42.849 --> 09:45.116
And that's exactly
what's gonna happen, baby.

09:45.118 --> 09:48.053
I'm in this band
because i believe in you.

09:48.055 --> 09:50.188
You and me--we can write
great songs together.

09:50.190 --> 09:52.290
- No, we can't. I can't write.
- Gigi, yes, we can.

09:52.292 --> 09:53.692
- Think about it.
- Okay.

09:53.694 --> 09:55.694
I write most of the riffs
that your dad uses.

09:55.696 --> 09:58.096
Even when he comes up
with his own melody lines,

09:58.098 --> 10:00.031
I'm the one
who makes them rock.

10:00.033 --> 10:03.568
We sit down,
start jamming every day,

10:03.570 --> 10:05.236
We're gonna come up
with something.

10:05.238 --> 10:06.871
I bet you got
a million great ideas

10:06.873 --> 10:08.873
In that gorgeous head
of yours.

10:08.875 --> 10:10.942
You know, i do have
a few good ideas.

10:10.944 --> 10:13.211
That song we played
the other night,

10:13.213 --> 10:15.547
You know, that just came
from my dad and i vocalizing,

10:15.549 --> 10:17.716
